<h3>
<a id="designer-templates" class="anchor" href="#designer-templates" aria-hidden="true"><span class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Interests</h3>
<p>I love picking up challenging projects using new tools. Java and C are always near and dear to my heart, but I've always enjoyed taking on a project with brand new technology, learning along the way. For the past year and a half I've been working on a network management web product for Nokia. The tech stack I'm currently most familiar is Java 8 with the latest Spring 4 and Angular. In addition to programming, I love running and drinking coffee.</p>
